{"tid":1344210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日有鄧炳強呢條友，義士只會越危險，黑警濫權只會越嚴重","createTime":"2019-07-21T21:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T21:40:27.000Z","uid":36775,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"360f03d7f4dce4db55bf4f48782cbb2dcecce52a","tid":1344210,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:04:26.000Z","msg":"講咗咁耐都未招呼呢條友<br />\n<br />\n盧狗係半退休狀態<br />\n<br />\n有傳612、旺角一役係由狗二哥鄧炳強策劃同指揮<br />\n<br />\n雖然咩飛依然係盧狗，但鄧係實際上嘅一哥<br />\n<br />\n仲未坐正都已經咁狠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拎三十幾粒子彈射義士</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>加以催淚煙作掩護來射義士嘅仆街野</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n比佢坐正義士只會更危險<br />\n<br />\n再睇下佢講野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5d78oOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5d78oOX.png&h=9c00285d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友無底線，坐正每次坐底出橡膠子彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇下佢履歷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ocz3Qo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ocz3Qo.png&h=1fbd1294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷疑紅底<br />\n- 國家行政學院同公安大學學習<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">也懷疑係其中一個原因點解都唔成立獨立調查委員會</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n升職快過火箭<br />\n- 一定做事心狠手辣先升得咁快<br />\n<br />\n副處長（行動）<br />\n- 行動=武官，姐係禿鷹戈款，唔同盧狗係文官出身，但唔係文指揮槍個後果大家知，做野一定係辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合其他post，鄧炳強曾任元朗指揮官，有可能同今晚元朗黑社會劈友有關係<br />\n<br />\n佢成功做咗兩樣無人敢做嘅事<br />\n1. 開槍<br />\n2. 公開警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一日有佢，狗只會放肆，前線手足只會越危險</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時分分鐘要懷念盧蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d92bd114248fb7867acfedef5135d8b96456a6b","tid":1344210,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:04:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f65b820855dec5a3825c013e691d58eef373b03f","tid":1344210,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:06:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e248d6d428e0fbb764eab47ffe3474a57b3c8977","tid":1344210,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"冤有頭 債有主，點都係蘆狗首當其衝，何況黑警無一個係無辜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9380ae6bc15c62eb53d41400c63a1984b2e1eab","tid":1344210,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e248d6d428e0fbb764eab47ffe3474a57b3c8977","tid":1344210,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"冤有頭 債有主，點都係蘆狗首當其衝，何況黑警無一個係無辜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:08:03.000Z","msg":"蘆狗係傀儡, 仲要就退休<br />\n唔可以比2哥上位"},{"pid":"b4cad3b4023209f8262fc8334877cb7915640b3b","tid":1344210,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:09:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1245370/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1245370/page/1</a> 上個月已講"},{"pid":"7258ad1a733e4890c42591265760dc0e88ad03f9","tid":1344210,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9380ae6bc15c62eb53d41400c63a1984b2e1eab","tid":1344210,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e248d6d428e0fbb764eab47ffe3474a57b3c8977","tid":1344210,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"冤有頭 債有主，點都係蘆狗首當其衝，何況黑警無一個係無辜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 